\paragraph{SR008}
  \begin{description}
  \item [Statement] 
    \textit{ As to avoid potential abuse, chat messages shall have a reasonable maximum length.}
  \item [Priority] \textit{A}
\end{description}

  STATMENT documents used in document sharing shall not exceed a certain size limit
  PRIORIY A

  STATEMEMT Functions like recording,mute,sub-moderation rights and invitation will be transfered to a merged confernce
  PRIORITY B

  STATEMENT To merge two conferences, the moderator of both conferences shall be able to link them.
  PRIORITY B
